          <p><a href="https://sebiik.github.io/community.axoloti.com.backup/u/sirsicksik">@SirSickSik</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>try out my stackable scope (sss/disp), this has an independent sync trigger input.<br>Then use only one of the two oscillators to sync both and send the two oscillators to the input pins.<br>Also got several bigger scopes for bass and k-rate frequency oscillators.</p>
